import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom/client'
import './index.css'
import App from './App'
import { Provider } from 'react-redux'
import store from './redux/store/store'

ReactDOM.render (
    <Provider store={store}>
      <App />
    </Provider>,
    document.getElementById('root')
  );

root.render(<App />)
